data.description:
Step into the comfort of this inviting poolside home, highlighting a pristine pool and screened lanai. Constructed with durable CBS, this home offers a generous front living room and kitchen area complete with a convenient kitchen bar for additional dining space. French doors adorn the family, master, and dining rooms, seamlessly connecting indoor and outdoor living spaces, where your private pool area awaits just beyond the screened door in the fenced yard. Enjoy peace of mind with recent updates including a composition roof installed in 2016, a new dishwasher in 2023, and a replaced coil in the A/C unit in 2022. With no HOA, this property offers flexibility and freedom.Relax in the spacious primary bedroom featuring a large closet with built-ins, while a separate den/bonus space adjacent to the third bedroom provides additional living flexibility. The third bedroom, with its generous walk-in closet, is conveniently split from the other two bedrooms.

Additional updates include new gutters installed in 2022, and new tiles in 2nd bedroom adding to the overall appeal and functionality of this remarkable property.
